{"tid":968241,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet跨年擁抱獨缺Irene　可愛忙內上網求神手：把姐姐P上去","createTime":"2019-01-04T05:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T15:47:26.000Z","uid":74065,"like":90,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b9190bd98f4559242c6545cb78c916b304ec20","tid":968241,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:39:28.000Z","msg":"南韓女團Red Velvet甜美外表和舞台魅力圈粉無數，已是現今KPOP當紅女團之一。她們受邀參加跨年夜的《MBC歌謠大祭典》演出，在新年來臨那一刻彼此擁抱慶祝。不過隊長Irene當晚因為有其他行程不得不缺席倒數時刻，成員Yeri便在IG上徵求神手，把Irene給P上去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3809/3809278.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3809%2F3809278.jpg&h=e909f08d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Red Velvet跨年擁抱少了Irene，Yeri求網友幫忙P圖。（圖／翻攝自Red Velvet IG）<br />\n<br />\n在跨年夜舉辦的《MBC歌謠大祭典》，最後Ending時所有藝人聚集在台上，彼此擁抱慶祝新年。不過Red Velvet的隊長Irene因為有其他行程必須先離開，剩下的四位成員瑟琪、Yeri、Joy和Wendy一起擁抱著跨年，畫面非常溫馨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3809/d3809277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3809%2Fd3809277.jpg&h=a8802258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Red Velvet五名成員感情好。（圖／翻攝自Red Velvet IG）<br />\n老么Yeri在官方instagram上公開了四人擁抱的照片，並寫下：「希望有神手luv（粉絲暱稱）把柱現姐姐（Irene本名）P上去。」歌迷們也完成她的願望，瘋狂上傳各種P圖，其中也不乏搞笑之作，也讓成員們在IG限時動態回應道：「看得非常開心，不愧是ReVeluv（粉絲名稱），怎麼如此討人喜愛。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3809/d3809271.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3809%2Fd3809271.jpg&h=6eef2bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3809/d3809274.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3809%2Fd3809274.jpg&h=260f25bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3809/d3809273.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3809%2Fd3809273.jpg&h=2cca2ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3809/d3809270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3809%2Fd3809270.jpg&h=a2452b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求魔牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11310427fa9ab6dc288e5584ce39b2266eecf54b","tid":968241,"uid":223790,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb1bf229d3f09c0d909c3eb5986ac1f37a96783f","tid":968241,"uid":223790,"like":7,"dislike":33,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:40:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8c5b8ede1fe4c7edf94fe1bdae0828e19d4bcf0","tid":968241,"uid":223790,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4053a9638ce59a16cc7bd7db1f187003b4ba0a91","tid":968241,"uid":223790,"like":13,"dislike":17,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69b5f9c9cdbc2b7a3ee2e3f80887e4186d40155b","tid":968241,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:42:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1baf82073c5886d674da2ed105123b08b95a7398","tid":968241,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"盲反會說她們不和"},{"pid":"0091d03acd311b0b721696f2d262ad200c8b043d","tid":968241,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T06:08:04.000Z","msg":"留名睇6永條弱智金剛棒"},{"pid":"708b3590e08e07ec2b7c240fd95f05a2782558f1","tid":968241,"uid":52073,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主點睇你老友邊伯乜柒係咁入你d post到搞搞陣"},{"pid":"a8e9dd6564ee79331efbefcf841845468cfa2b0a","tid":968241,"uid":213300,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T06:14:17.000Z","msg":"點解頭五個comment唔見曬嘅"},{"pid":"5c6